OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSoon turning
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain moving
OL,7,Fsoutheastwards through this evening
OL,8,Fand overnight, turning heavy in
OL,9,Fplaces. Tending to become drier by
OL,10,Fdawn with some clearer spells
OL,11,Fdeveloping. Another muggy night to
OL,12,Fcome.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with perhaps
OL,15,Fthe odd spot of rain, however cloud
OL,16,Fwill break up, leading to a bright
OL,17,Fafternoon. Feeling a touch fresher but
OL,18,Fstill warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
