OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure builds across the region
OL,7,Fbringing plenty of dry and sunny
OL,8,Fweather. Temperatures increasing by
OL,9,Fday and night with hot and humid
OL,10,Fconditions developing early next week.
